OL,5, British ports have described Grant     
OL,6, Shapps' new pay plans for the ferry    
OL,7, industry as "unworkable".              
OL,9,FThe transport secretary has urged ports
OL,10,Fto block ferries from docking if they  
OL,11,Fdo not pay their crew the UK minimum   
OL,12,Fwage, with plans to create new laws.   
OL,14,FThe move comes after P&O Ferries sacked
OL,15,F800 of its staff without notice and    
OL,16,Freplaced with them with agency workers.
OL,18,FBut the boss of the ferry ports trade  
OL,19,Fbody raised concerns the government was
OL,20,F"rushing to find a solution".          
